{
  "title": "查看虚拟机里的Centos7的IP",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这里之所以是查看下IP ，是我们后面要建一个Centos远程工具Xshell 连接Centos的时候，需要IP地址，所以我们这里先</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">学会查看虚拟机里的Centos7的IP地址</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">首先我们登录操作系统 用户名root 密码 123456</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">然后我们输入ip查询命名 ip addr &nbsp;也可以输入 ifconfig查看ip，但此命令会出现3个条目，centos的ip地址是ens33条目中的inet值。<img src=\"quiver-image-url/AD2E20DDB5FA799A20E3F182DFD99210.jpg\" title=\"1497185138263086154.jpg\" alt=\"aa.jpg\" width=\"672\" height=\"267\" style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: zoom-in; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">发现 ens33 没有 inet 这个属性，那么就没法通过IP地址连接虚拟机。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">接着来查看ens33网卡的配置： vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens33 &nbsp; 注意vi后面加空格</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">vi是Linux内置的文本编辑器命令 打开文件的意思</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/EC4A1A651C0989D00E69346787A5A61C.jpg\" title=\"1497185328169099657.jpg\" alt=\"bb.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: zoom-in; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"483\" height=\"488\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">从配置清单中可以发现 CentOS 7 默认是不启动网卡的（ONBOOT=no）。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">把这一项改为YES（ONBOOT=yes），</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/1602909C0457EF9E630974EFDD85549B.jpg\" title=\"1497185415060083062.jpg\" alt=\"cc.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: zoom-in; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"485\" height=\"504\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">然后按 Esc 退出 &nbsp;再出入命令 :wq &nbsp;再按Enter即可 &nbsp;（备注 :wq 是保存然后退出的意思 后面会专门讲下vi）</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">然后重启网络服务： sudo service network restart&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/BE6CA4B5FBD76B09A8CC5829C6BFFF85.jpg\" title=\"1497185587029032526.jpg\" alt=\"ee.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: zoom-in; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"340\" height=\"38\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">然后我们再输入 &nbsp;ip addr 命令</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/FFC8C719E35D351DF20B2F27A38EAF89.jpg\" title=\"1497185609966089924.jpg\" alt=\"ff.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: zoom-in; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"563\" height=\"201\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这里 inet属性显示了 虚拟机里的IP &nbsp;192.168.1.107 &nbsp;(你们的可能和我不一样)</p>"
    }
  ]
}